      profil_p1: 'I am Argentine, and arrived in France at the end of 2022. In Argentina, I studied law. In France, I seized the opportunity to redirect my career and chose the BUT TC with a Client Relations specialisation on a work-study basis at IUT d\'Évry, in order to gain professional experience and a recognised qualification simultaneously.',
      profil_p2: 'This decision reflects my adaptability and my determination to build a solid commercial career in a new environment, in French, by quickly mastering the professional codes of the sector.',
      profil_h2_alternance: 'My work-study',
      profil_p_alternance: 'My work-study placement at <strong>Global Blue Tax Free</strong> has allowed me to take on the role of Junior Account Manager: managing a client portfolio, commercial prospecting, performance monitoring and B2B relationship development. This hands-on experience is the common thread running through my commercial skills development.',
      timeline_title: 'Journey',
      tl1_h3: 'BUT Business & Marketing',
      tl1_p: 'IUT d\'Évry — Work-study programme, Client Relations specialisation',
      tl2_h3: 'Junior Account Manager',
