      interests_sub: 'My interests and passions',
      interest1_h3: 'Digital Entrepreneurship & Tech Ecosystem',
      interest1_p: 'Passionate about building web projects and launching Minimum Viable Products (MVPs). I enjoy turning ideas into concrete solutions and quickly testing new concepts on the market.',
      interest2_h3: 'Web Development & No-Code Tools',
      interest2_p: 'I continuously explore new technological tools. I design and deploy landing pages and showcase websites (via GitHub, Vercel, or no-code solutions) to optimise the online presence of various projects.',
      interest3_h3: 'Social Media & Content Creation',
      interest3_p: 'Fascinated by virality mechanics, I manage online communities and create engaging content. This allows me to concretely analyse algorithms and understand what captures the attention of a large audience.',

