      comp1_eyebrow: 'Competency 1',
      comp1_title: 'Marketing',
      comp1_subtitle: 'Building a complex or innovative commercial offer',
      comp1_sc1: 'Diagnosing the environment by understanding social and ecological challenges',
      comp1_sc1_c1_title: 'Creation of the senior mobile app "Part\'Âge"',
      comp1_sc1_c1_desc: 'As part of a business creation project, we had to design an innovative offer responding to a real market need while integrating current societal challenges. With my team, we identified the social isolation of elderly people as a key issue. We conducted market research, analysed the expectations of senior users, and designed the "Part\'Âge" mobile app to foster friendly encounters. This project allowed me to turn a societal challenge into a concrete marketing opportunity.',
      comp1_sc1_c2_title: 'Marketing study – Impact of AI on students\' daily lives',
      comp1_sc1_c2_desc: 'As part of a marketing study, we analysed the impact of artificial intelligence on students\' habits to understand how a technological innovation transforms a usage environment. We conducted qualitative and quantitative research with individual interviews. This project strengthened my ability to observe environmental changes and integrate societal impacts into a marketing analysis.',
      comp1_sc1_c3_title: 'Carrefour Crisis Communication',
      comp1_sc1_c3_desc: 'In a marketing strategy exercise, we imagined handling a bad buzz around the fictional launch of an eco-friendly shampoo by Carrefour. We analysed consumer expectations regarding environmental transparency and designed a crisis communication strategy. This project helped me understand how ecological issues influence the perception of a commercial offer.',
      comp1_sc2: 'Conducting a market study in a complex environment',
      comp1_sc2_c1_title: 'Part\'Âge (complete market study)',
      comp1_sc2_c1_desc: 'As part of the Part\'Âge project, we conducted a comprehensive market study: sector potential analysis, demographic trends, specific target needs and competing solutions. This project allowed me to develop a structured market research methodology in a complex environment.',
      comp1_sc2_c2_title: 'AI / Students marketing study',
      comp1_sc2_c2_desc: 'We designed and conducted a qualitative and quantitative study on the impact of AI on student behaviour, including questionnaires and individual interviews. This project gave me hands-on experience in implementing a market study on an innovative topic.',
      comp1_sc2_c3_title: 'Schneider Electric B2B Market Presentation',
      comp1_sc2_c3_desc: 'We conducted an in-depth study of Schneider Electric\'s market: market structure, client profiles, trends, competition and value chain. This project helped me better understand the specifics of a complex B2B environment.',
      comp1_sc3: 'Implementing a marketing strategy in a complex environment',
      comp1_sc3_c1_title: 'Operational marketing strategy – Michel & Augustin',
      comp1_sc3_c1_desc: 'We developed a complete marketing strategy for Michel & Augustin: SWOT, targeting, positioning, marketing mix and 2024 product innovation. This project allowed me to design and structure a full marketing strategy in a competitive and dynamic environment.',
      comp1_sc3_c2_title: 'Carrefour Crisis Communication (eco product bad buzz)',
      comp1_sc3_c2_desc: 'We built a crisis communication strategy for Carrefour following a fictional bad buzz. We analysed the causes of the crisis and developed a plan to restore trust. This project helped me understand how to adapt a marketing strategy in a reputation-sensitive context.',
      comp1_sc3_c3_title: 'B2B Marketing Analysis – Peugeot',
      comp1_sc3_c3_desc: 'We analysed Peugeot\'s strategy in the professional market: positioning, targeting and marketing actions in the automotive sector. This project helped me better understand how to build a marketing strategy suited to an industrial market.',
      comp1_sc4: 'Designing an extended marketing mix for a complex offer',
      comp1_sc4_c1_title: 'Michel & Augustin (full marketing mix + product innovation)',
      comp1_sc4_c1_desc: 'We built a complete marketing mix integrating the 4Ps and a 2024 product innovation: product strategy, pricing policy, distribution and communication. This project allowed me to design a coherent and extended marketing mix integrating classic dimensions and an innovation logic.',
      comp1_sc4_c2_title: 'Part\'Âge (business model + complete offer)',
      comp1_sc4_c2_desc: 'We designed a complete senior mobile app offer by structuring the entire business model: value proposition, features, monetisation model and cost structure. This project allowed me to design an extended mix beyond the traditional 4Ps.',
      comp1_sc4_c3_title: 'Carrefour Crisis Communication (adapted mix in a sensitive situation)',
      comp1_sc4_c3_desc: 'We adapted a brand\'s marketing mix in a crisis context by identifying perceived inconsistencies and proposing communication and positioning adjustments. This project helped me understand how a marketing mix must be adjusted based on market reactions.',

