      comp2_sc2_c3_desc: 'We analysed negotiation mechanisms in the professional automotive sector: price adaptation by volume and agreement optimisation strategies. This project helped me understand negotiation logic in a complex B2B environment.',
      comp2_sc3: 'Mastering the legal and accounting aspects of the offer',
      comp2_sc3_c1_title: 'Sales interview – Ruckfield case',
      comp2_sc3_c1_desc: 'In the Ruckfield simulation, we integrated constraints related to product referencing and distribution conditions. This project helped me understand the legal and commercial aspects of a distribution relationship.',
