      comp2_sc3_c3_desc: 'In the Peugeot B2B study, we analysed the contractual specifics of the professional automotive sector, particularly volume purchase negotiation terms. This project allowed me to approach the economic and organisational aspects of an offer in a B2B context.',
      comp2_sc4: 'Using sales support tools (SSTs) effectively to convince',
