      comp2_sc4_c3_desc: 'In the Michel & Augustin project, we used structured slide decks to argue our strategic choices during the oral presentation. This project helped me understand the value of argumentation supports in building an effective commercial pitch.',
      comp2_sc5: 'Organising results tracking to improve commercial team performance',
      comp2_sc5_c1_title: 'Commercial Excel dashboard',
      comp2_sc5_c1_desc: 'We designed a continuous commercial performance tracking tool (revenue, KPIs, sales trends) to identify improvement areas and manage activity as a team. This project helped me understand the importance of performance tracking for effectively managing commercial activity.',
      comp2_sc5_c2_title: 'B2B Marketing – Schneider Electric',
      comp2_sc5_c2_desc: 'We studied how Schneider Electric structures and tracks its commercial performance through its value chain and client relationships. This project gave me a global view of performance management in a complex B2B environment.',
      comp2_sc5_c3_title: 'B2B Marketing – Peugeot',
      comp2_sc5_c3_desc: 'In the Peugeot study, we analysed volume, contract and client relationship tracking to adjust sales strategies. This project helped me grasp the importance of results tracking in a structured commercial environment.',
      comp2_sc6: 'Considering purchasing function challenges for the company\'s economic performance',
      comp2_sc6_c1_title: 'B2B Marketing – Peugeot',
      comp2_sc6_c1_desc: 'We analysed Peugeot\'s relationships with professional clients, integrating purchasing logic specific to the automotive sector. This project helped me better understand purchasing strategies and their impact on sales decisions and overall performance.',
      comp2_sc6_c2_title: 'B2B Marketing – Schneider Electric',
      comp2_sc6_c2_desc: 'In the Schneider Electric analysis, we understood that B2B clients\' purchasing decisions are driven by economic performance and cost optimisation. This project helped me better understand the challenges of the purchasing function in a complex B2B context.',
      comp2_sc6_c3_title: 'Sales interview – Ruckfield case',
